just_use admin_ops.go

# label: WORKHORSE
# role: supports feature — /admin/ops dashboard + /admin/health JSON + reset

Three surfaces share one data source: HTML dashboard (auto-refreshes every
10s), JSON health endpoint (consumed by cmd/health_check for triage), and
a POST reset that zeroes events/presence/ratelimit counters in one shot.
In-memory stats only — doesn't survive restart, which is the point.
